{"word":"μεγαλοπρεπής","slug":"μεγαλοπρεπής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μεγαλοπρεπής</b></el> <el>(μεγᾰλο-πρεπής, ές) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πρέπω'><el>πρέπω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>befitting a great man, magnificent</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic:— <el>τὸ μεγαλοπρεπές,  μεγαλοπρέπεια</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ῶς</el>, ionic <el>-έως</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>-έστερον</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>-έστατα</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}